SUMMARY:Philadelphia Connection Masonic Temple Tour
DESCRIPTION:Organized by: ['College Advancement']\\nCategory: Exhibit\\nPhi
 ladelphia Connection Masonic Temple Tour Saturday\, June 13\, 2026 at 11:0
 0 AM Masonic Temple1 N Broad StPhiladelphia\, PA 19107 RSVP here Join the 
 Philadelphia Connection Committee for an exclusive tour of the historic Ma
 sonic Temple\, in celebration of the nation's Semiquincentennial. Discover
  the enduring legacy of Masonic Founders like Washington and Franklin\, wh
 ose ideals of liberty and equality helped shape our democracy. Reconnect w
 ith fellow alumni as you explore this architectural masterpiece in the hea
 rt of the city. We look forward to seeing you there! Reconnect with fellow
  alumni during this experience\, then join us for an optional group lunch 
 after the tour to continue our conversations. Lunch venue details will be 
 shared very soon.\\nDetails: https://swatcentral.swarthmore.edu/?trumbaEmb
 ed=view%3Devent%26eventid%3D1397186024
