SUMMARY:Swarthmore Night on Broadway\, The Fear of 13
DESCRIPTION:Organized by: ['College Advancement']\\nCategory: Performance\\
 nSwarthmore Night on Broadway\, The Fear of 13 Post-show Q&A with star Adr
 ien Brody and members of The Fear of 13 creative team James Earl Jones Th
 eatre138 W 48th StreetNew York Get My Ticket The Fear of 13 is the true st
 ory of Nick Yarris — played by Adrien Brody — a man who spent 22 years
  on death row before being exonerated by DNA evidence.   As an alumni vol
 unteer for Swarthmore\, you have access to orchestra tickets before they o
 pen to the broader community. Know a fellow alum who’d love to get more 
 involved? Bring them along. This is a great way to introduce them to our v
 olunteer community. Space for this event is extremely limited\, and we exp
 ect it to fill up quickly. If you're thinking about joining us\, don't wai
 t — reserve your discounted ticket today\\nDetails: https://swatcentral.
 swarthmore.edu/?trumbaEmbed=view%3Devent%26eventid%3D1402778070
