SUMMARY:SwatWalks: D.C.
DESCRIPTION:Organized by: ['College Advancement']\\nCategory: Recreation-Ge
 neral\\nSwatWalks: D.C. Rock Creek Park Nature Center and Planetarium5200 
 Glover Rd NWWashington\, DC 20015 Step outside and connect with your local
  community through SwatWalks\, our new alumni-led series of outdoor social
  strolls! We are kicking off our very first outing in the D.C. area with a
  private walk in Rock Creek Park\, specially curated for the Swarthmore co
 mmunity\, led by the Rock Creek Conservancy. Please join host Ethan Landis
  ’84\, fellow alumni\, and your guests for a wonderful morning of conver
 sation and fresh air. This walk is perfect for all ages and abilities. Whe
 ther you want some fresh air\, lively conversation\, or a great reason to 
 get outside\, this is your morning. Bring your Swat spirit — let's walk\
 , talk\, and enjoy the outdoors together. RSVP! Program8:15 a.m. Meet in f
 ront of Rock Creek Park Nature Center8:30 a.m. Walk departs We look forwar
 d to celebrating the first day of summer with you at Rock Creek Park. Plea
 se remember to bring water\, a hat\, and sunscreen for the walk. Warmly\,S
 warthmore Alumni Engagement\\nDetails: https://swatcentral.swarthmore.edu/
 ?trumbaEmbed=view%3Devent%26eventid%3D1402778072
URL:https://swatcentral.swarthmore.edu/?trumbaEmbed=view%3Devent%26eventid%
 3D1402778072
CATEGORIES:Recreation-General
END:VEVENT
