 ys and Thursdays in Sci 101 from 12-1:30pm. Lunch will be provided. Throug
 h this interactive presentation\, participants will learn key strategies f
 or professional written and verbal communication\, including email etiquet
 te\, meeting participation\, and clear expectation-setting with supervisor
