SUMMARY:Peter van de Kamp Observatory Open House - Cancelled 6/9/26
DESCRIPTION:Organized by: ['Physics and Astronomy']\\nCategory: Open House\
 \nUnfortunately\, the open house event scheduled for June 9 has been cance
 lled due to insufficient staffing. We apologize for this notice and hope f
 or a successful July 14 event. The Physics and Astronomy department hosts 
 a telescope open house on the second Tuesday of each month at the Peter va
 n de Kamp Observatory on the roof of the Science Center. Directions are av
 ailable at www.swarthmore.edu/peter-van-de-kamp-observatory/directions. Th
 e open house hours are 8:00 p.m. to 9:00 p.m. during standard time and 9:0
 0 p.m. to 10:00 p.m. during daylight savings time. The SC-1 exterior door 
 under the breezeway will be open 10 minutes before the start time. The roo
 ftop access door will open at the event start time. If the weather is bad\
 , the open house will be cancelled by 5:00 p.m.\, and an announcement will
  be posted on the Physics and Astronomy department website and the College
  calendar. Check https://www.swarthmore.edu/physics-astronomy on the day 
 of the open house if the weather is questionable Open to the public. \\nD
 etails: https://swatcentral.swarthmore.edu/?trumbaEmbed=view%3Devent%26eve
 ntid%3D1364584548
LOCATION:Science Center Peter Van de Kamp Observatory\, Science Center Obse
 rvatory Computer Room
URL:https://swatcentral.swarthmore.edu/?trumbaEmbed=view%3Devent%26eventid%
 3D1364584548
CATEGORIES:Open House
END:VEVENT
