 or help so you can move from overwhelm into action. Presented by Simone Co
 llins\, Director of Counseling & Psychological Services\, and Josh Ellow\,
  Associate Director\, Wellness Assessment & Compliance & Alcohol & Other D
 rug Counselor.\\nDetails: https://swatcentral.swarthmore.edu/?trumbaEmbed=
 view%3Devent%26eventid%3D1395671885
URL:https://swatcentral.swarthmore.edu/?trumbaEmbed=view%3Devent%26eventid%
 3D1395671885
CATEGORIES:Lecture/Panel Discussion
END:VEVENT
